      "kind": "round-trip",
      "description": "Over a two-island terrain (A1 header; B2:D4 block; empty row 5; F6:F7 island): last-used-row=7, last-used-column=6 (a NUMBER string, not a letter), first-empty-row=5 (the scan finds the interior gap, not lastRow+1). All geometry results are strings.",
      "expr": {
        "and": [
          {
            "equals": [
              {
                "$var": "lastRow"
              },
              "7"
            ]
          },
          {
            "equals": [
              {
                "$var": "lastCol"
